text: Fontenelle Abbey may refer to: * Abbey of Saint Wandrille, also known as Fontenelle Abbey, a Benedictine monastery in Saint-Wandrille-Rançon, Seine- Maritime, France * Fontenelle Abbey (Nord), a Cistercian nunnery in Maing, Nord, France ==See also== * Fontenelles Abbey, an Augustinian monastery in La Roche-sur-Yon, Vendée, France
title: Fontenelle Abbey (disambiguation)
